Write a Program to find the smallest element in the Array

Input: 
n = 5
1 3 5 7 8
Ouput Expected:
1

Example 2
Input:
n = 8
5 7 34 67 2 56 5 8
Output:2

program:
package practice_java;
import java.util.Scanner;
public class demo {
	   public static void main(String[] args){
		           Scanner S=new Scanner(System.in);
		           System.out.println("Enter the size");
		           int n=S.nextInt();
		           System.out.println("Enter the array");
		           int [] arr=new int[n];
		           
		           for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
		               arr[i]=S.nextInt();
		           }
		           int min=arr[0];
		           for(int i=1;i<n;i++){
		               if(min>arr[i]){
		                   min=arr[i];
		               }
		               
		           }
		           System.out.print("Miniimum Number"+min);
		           
		       }
		   }
    
